strings:
<se_low>Yangus: Awright, Brains!
Can I beg a bit of info off ya again!?

<se_def>Brains: Ah, Yangus. How are you doing?
Did you manage to find the ship?
<se_low>Yangus: Yeah! But 'ave you ever 'eard o' this thing called the Moonshadow 'arp? We need it, desp'rate like.

<se_def>Brains: The Moonshadow harp?
Hm, I've got a feeling there was once a
piece of treasure in Ascantha called that.

<se_low>Yangus: Nice one, Brains!
I knew you'd come up wiv the goods!
I'd better get a move on to Ascantha then!
See ya!

<se_def>Brains: ...Er, bye then!
Always in a rush, eh!?
